{"tid":1616662,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"萬聖變裝指南","createTime":"2019-10-03T13:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T14:30:54.000Z","uid":122827,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"49d4772e6d90596518c2e012af656dcb02ab2172","tid":1616662,"uid":122827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:30:09.000Z","msg":"今個十月 又係一年一度既萬聖節<br />\n海洋公園同迪士尼都已經開放比大家玩萬聖節限定嘅設施<br />\n咁去得玩唔化妝唔扮鬼梗係冇乜意思啦<br />\n所以我就揀左下面幾款造型比大家參巧 有土豪裝同平民裝可以揀<br />\n<br />\n土豪裝<br />\n支持本土製造同有D錢既可以試下:<br />\n<img src=\"https://gimy.cc/upload/vod/20190510-3/e967f5ea95e5a6867192ccf7e3bfed80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgimy.cc%2Fupload%2Fvod%2F20190510-3%2Fe967f5ea95e5a6867192ccf7e3bfed80.jpg&h=9d2f82a2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n(那夜凌晨，我坐上了旺角開往大埔的紅VAN)<br />\n<br />\n平民裝<br />\n冇乜錢又想參與下可以試下呢D:<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thewrap.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/scream-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thewrap.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Fscream-1.jpg&h=bb9ed17c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n(搞乜鬼奪命雜作)<br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-qHkVatshwmA/WcqlrJ5LSeI/AAAAAAAAukI/60IishHmw3Y405VLA46bB_eucG8WYMQ_QCEwYBhgL/s1600/DSC09754.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-qHkVatshwmA%2FWcqlrJ5LSeI%2FAAAAAAAAukI%2F60IishHmw3Y405VLA46bB_eucG8WYMQ_QCEwYBhgL%2Fs1600%2FDSC09754.JPG&h=81b400c7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n(恐懼鬥室)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ruten.com.tw/s3/0ef/8bd/ralphlauren168/d/84/cf/21845931631823_808.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ruten.com.tw%2Fs3%2F0ef%2F8bd%2Fralphlauren168%2Fd%2F84%2Fcf%2F21845931631823_808.jpeg&h=ae728cf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(千與千尋)<br />\n<br />\n除左港島區既海洋公園同離島既迪士尼 全香港唔同地區都有慶祝活動 希望大家今個十月玩得開心"},{"pid":"25d0befb68a294e3d027289b5de40be321b5092a","tid":1616662,"uid":35134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:30:54.000Z","msg":"Trick or treat <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}